{"tid":233280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[死場]荃灣「死城」海濱廣場疑辦國際學校","createTime":"2017-05-07T12:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T11:12:58.000Z","uid":29609,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"34b308b736f216b0afc7837c1bcd42b6b433d496","tid":233280,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:22:46.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人敢入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係好似封咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/863239/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F863239%2F%20&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d669a62a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F863239%2F%20&h=950889c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/863239/ </a><br />\n荃灣「死城」海濱廣場疑辦國際學校，有報道指，「鋪王」鄧成波兒子鄧耀昇計劃與多位名人合作，於丟空多年的荃灣海濱廣場開辦國際中小學，包括莎莎國際老闆郭少明、殯儀大王梁津煥記接班人梁家強，以及多名有營運社福機構經驗的退休人士等，隨著鄉議局主席劉業強淡出，計劃由鄧耀昇主導，並於2018年開校。<br />\n<br />\n海濱廣場之全盛期為1990年至1997年，曾經擁有電影院海濱戲院、佔地三層的永安百貨（部分後來闢作老人院）、電子遊戲機中心以及美食廣場等。開幕初年人流不俗。然而，由於交通方面相對較荃灣市中心不便，又不設免費接駁巴士線來往市區藉以吸引顧客。<br />\n<br />\n海濱廣場三樓主要為溜冰場，與四樓連貫，於1990年開業，是全香港第二座座落在大型商場內的溜冰場，亦是當年新界唯一一座擁有溜冰場的商場。及至同區的荃灣廣場等大型商場相繼出現溜冰場後，海濱廣場溜冰場的人流開始回落。<br />\n<br />\n鄧成波2015年時向宏安購入荃灣商場海濱廣場，作價約8.2億元，平均呎價約3391元，預計作翻新及長線收租，原業主持貨三年，物業期內升值約六成二。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣海濱廣場2013年曾計劃發展成「市區OUTLET」，但2015年被收購後一直丟空至今。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/issue/286/thumbnail/b1966bfdcd6e5c06be50f01483a3633b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fissue%2F286%2Fthumbnail%2Fb1966bfdcd6e5c06be50f01483a3633b.jpg&h=779bc67d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/481026/xlarge/400519604fb77f91a73fb17607a1d884.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F481026%2Fxlarge%2F400519604fb77f91a73fb17607a1d884.jpg&h=de39300d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/481027/xlarge/e1303123b36d8582416607013355a9b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F481027%2Fxlarge%2Fe1303123b36d8582416607013355a9b4.jpg&h=b4cc5924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/480627/xlarge/cb345257df05c56202c364a952e31d0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F480627%2Fxlarge%2Fcb345257df05c56202c364a952e31d0d.jpg&h=a53a3fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/480997/xlarge/24785d45e1a22f8b5dd243379e783ef1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F480997%2Fxlarge%2F24785d45e1a22f8b5dd243379e783ef1.jpg&h=b54821a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/481025/xlarge/af7c488971532178b3fcae2dce537b92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F481025%2Fxlarge%2Faf7c488971532178b3fcae2dce537b92.jpg&h=eabe16ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/481024/xlarge/b184c5e271a42e085a9ae8980e472fc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F481024%2Fxlarge%2Fb184c5e271a42e085a9ae8980e472fc5.jpg&h=97bdd205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/481157/xlarge/b1749b762114671e44bd7b03429aa75d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F481157%2Fxlarge%2Fb1749b762114671e44bd7b03429aa75d.jpg&h=5e5705cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"102bee79e891a14b928e5c63f31120782083297f","tid":233280,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036fcb198204c878bad7cc69afecb981f020ef91","tid":233280,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"好似切爾諾貝爾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2245ff4c23bb19afcea6d0ba36eb004bdf5fcc","tid":233280,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"前街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b029e7d0f2f6187f08daffd02a31a30f75ea358d","tid":233280,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪真係咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b24ecb98476a100330e315e85791b1332eb0f4","tid":233280,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個向到學溜冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951c2c2f32b7702e269e60ba830dbb31239c3700","tid":233280,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"其實個死因係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照計附近啲人都係度架"},{"pid":"637ae0a67a535190cf588477749ddf64f9931594","tid":233280,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"之前死剩溜冰場嗰時已經好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00f3e87150c1714364932410e64c58241a8c405","tid":233280,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:08:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6bc632d99910f08deb620e247bfeec654089de9","tid":233280,"uid":41683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"前街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n四年前搬走左<br />\n最後果張相係food court黎 封左唔知有冇十年 連𨋢都搭唔到上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他幾張都差唔多係咁 不過唔會完全冇人<br />\n成個商場連地下有9層 基本上得最底4,5層會有人類 因為有百佳同麥當勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221b51bec100ba565ef8be3a1f43a0748da1e846","tid":233280,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪真係咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前頂樓仲有開燈會同frd上去玩卡<br />\n後尾燈都唔開就恐怖到唔敢上去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到搬走前淨係會去同一層既m記同百佳 其他層完全冇再上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb995a95cc517e5f6a284ea99397a1f6ae2568aa","tid":233280,"uid":2959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"入去玩running man"},{"pid":"34292e66e8019c3d0f70a73963e21286dac84ac4","tid":233280,"uid":23829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:16:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得有一排m記上一層開過一間好似冒險樂園咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfe4f17fca43dfdd5dd7802c5d901035d4c86cc","tid":233280,"uid":45985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"咁多人住海濱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個幼稚園係海濱 成日食個間麥當勞"},{"pid":"bee6d1cdb663f4735d319ce1918cba16d088c649","tid":233280,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"去過幾次食曲奇船長自助餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8be58e635cf7d56f4800988e7456b1ac0a3cf5d","tid":233280,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實個死因係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照計附近啲人都係度架</blockquote><br />\n海濱廣場（英語：Riviera Plaza）位於香港荃灣區海濱花園內，於1990年11月落成，商場樓高9層（地下及1-8樓）和設有2層地庫，總樓面為242,685平方呎，並提供171個車位。商場曾經擁有佔地3層的永安百貨、翰騰閣酒家以及美食廣場等眾多設施。然而因交通不便，以及居民亦甚少到該商場消費，商場於1997年後開始出現大量店舖凋空的情況。商場於2012年11月成功以5.08億港元售出，2013年11月後一直封閉至今。</blockquote><br />\n唔係話死過人係花槽跟住鬧鬼無人去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d089324edb0fcae544f829ea7350a5272bca7e","tid":233280,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實個死因係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照計附近啲人都係度架</blockquote><br />\n海濱廣場（英語：Riviera Plaza）位於香港荃灣區海濱花園內，於1990年11月落成，商場樓高9層（地下及1-8樓）和設有2層地庫，總樓面為242,685平方呎，並提供171個車位。商場曾經擁有佔地3層的永安百貨、翰騰閣酒家以及美食廣場等眾多設施。然而因交通不便，以及居民亦甚少到該商場消費，商場於1997年後開始出現大量店舖凋空的情況。商場於2012年11月成功以5.08億港元售出，2013年11月後一直封閉至今。</blockquote><br />\n唔係話死過人係花槽跟住鬧鬼無人去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對面已經係墳場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513a40952741c48a4d05bf09855f75a53897dba0","tid":233280,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"去過一次溜冰<br />\n之後冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec62767bba0622175781a644d1465cd9540cbe89","tid":233280,"uid":87134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"正正住喺隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我陣係想要返個m記炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167273d556df0594f3752fae133c6e5d2cc00476","tid":233280,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"1990住過海濱<br />\n<br />\n過陣算係啱啱入伙<br />\n<br />\n有幸見證個商場都熱鬧嘅一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da60648effbcb89bf7c52e2c6196a3579632fe0","tid":233280,"uid":56775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"好似打l4d咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791fefad3fdf8bae6899318308381fb631224d1d","tid":233280,"uid":66254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"on9交通唔方便 個停車場又細又窄又陰暗<br />\n海濱入面地面同平台已經有足夠鋪仔 大公司唔荒會開喺嗰個位<br />\n唔收皮至奇"},{"pid":"353f804fc6653483d609f5deb1986b584bb16e9b","tid":233280,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實個死因係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照計附近啲人都係度架</blockquote><br />\n海濱廣場（英語：Riviera Plaza）位於香港荃灣區海濱花園內，於1990年11月落成，商場樓高9層（地下及1-8樓）和設有2層地庫，總樓面為242,685平方呎，並提供171個車位。商場曾經擁有佔地3層的永安百貨、翰騰閣酒家以及美食廣場等眾多設施。然而因交通不便，以及居民亦甚少到該商場消費，商場於1997年後開始出現大量店舖凋空的情況。商場於2012年11月成功以5.08億港元售出，2013年11月後一直封閉至今。</blockquote><br />\n唔係話死過人係花槽跟住鬧鬼無人去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對面已經係墳場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要問題係一定要靠街客但個交通注定好難有街客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06987900e992b0917cbea30b95f0e9e8e69f3a27","tid":233280,"uid":26038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"而家個場係一間鋪都無？<br />\n咁係咪得個保安"},{"pid":"1f7abd3b8e91cbe92db97fbee4b365ae595c931c","tid":233280,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:59:22.000Z","msg":"搞outlet可能work既"},{"pid":"8af7d49ae1c7dc768048513dc976985f81e39ab7","tid":233280,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"呢到個保安會唔會好好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d2fc8f57352e4c07cf98c60e8e19f35071f8a8","tid":233280,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"好似之前話有鬼"},{"pid":"5d609a4c021e66687181f2c7af35ba2bf1a8a168","tid":233280,"uid":29609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢到個保安會唔會好好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得之前有人話去探險 探探下見到保安 兩邊都嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保安話黐線做乜會有人喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b6c73fa9dc967e2e0bcbfad5e90ef269557e23","tid":233280,"uid":4000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"當年唔敢去food court 個層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12f737252e79e3000bb6c25f8e75987fb8c900a","tid":233280,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似切爾諾貝爾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3598292d0904b2b7afba7de77439a4ca5f5069c6","tid":233280,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"個場都叫響住宅區之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\