kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎果度氣氛真係幾恐怖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要唔開燈 咁大聽自己腳步聲都夠恐怖"},{"pid":"f2858dff272f1c0f0286c9aeb77d6c593edfb4de","tid":233280,"uid":33281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"有冇睇過[第八層地獄]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5f15347153f7b69c165025c6e87e974dc12c0b","tid":233280,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"之前住左十幾年 而家海灣仲旺過海濱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a40789a5ccc095322323c380c6ef8749a625e6","tid":233280,"uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"國際學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca6d6b602c987afc5371e3a22fbca223224a9b7","tid":233280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似之前話有鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世上邊會有鬼<br />\n<br />\n人仲恐怖過鬼"},{"pid":"338ef75ba07f5d89a90303dca1728c76468f349c","tid":233280,"uid":5382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"住咗海濱二十年<br />\n細個成日去海濱廣場玩<br />\n記得細個嗰時約過女仔喺海濱廣場溜冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲記得個溜冰場會播腎仔首赤城千葉同twins啲歌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後期就執嗰陣都開始少去<br />\n得返間百佳 老麥同屈臣係多人<br />\n仲有幾間文具鋪同嗰啲音樂學校<br />\n變咗成班廢老喺度涼冷氣<br />\n上面foodcourt以前都多嘢食<br />\n後期收曬皮 個場臨收皮嘅時候我都上過一次foodcourt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同以前一模一樣<br />\n都幾恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487b0dab2d7f888ca7c8f09944bf6c476707ce56","tid":233280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇睇過[第八層地獄]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無, 講黎聽下"},{"pid":"0b0aca20c1c3a4258b7edb7757745de69bad29f5","tid":233280,"uid":26038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國際學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以鬼治鬼"},{"pid":"c930f9e88e84b00c6cf00412d7ea1c6085901d04","tid":233280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>國際學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以鬼治鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞得國際學校, 就成幢拆左起過啦"},{"pid":"422d4a3a85b7d4cea1320c2a65771be6a209385b","tid":233280,"uid":33281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇睇過[第八層地獄]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無, 講黎聽下</blockquote><br />\n紙言故仔 個題材就係用呢到 講呢到變左海濱大學"},{"pid":"b1ad2ca2598a88140ae36a4fdf438565e3123308","tid":233280,"uid":5729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"其實而家仲入唔入得去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d4184f7580228df9aa250efb7606bbad756e87","tid":233280,"uid":31353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"搞到我有啲想入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9d70816d29d4d4c2548d018d3a6de3e32a1933","tid":233280,"uid":18811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"好似話8樓大家樂