9eb0ce955b53","tid":233280,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住緊海濱<br />\n講真以前有m記又有溜冰場上面有啲野食下真係幾好<br />\n依家得番海灣有兩間茶樓 有啲鋪頭同百佳<br />\n食個方面海濱又唔多選擇 又冇m記<br />\n有時真係口痕想食m記都要出去買<br />\n行出去西鐵都係10分鐘有啲樹遮下太陽<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊好似又有多個商場開</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d439568d7f57442a2649ac6a39d562c8cde5494","tid":233280,"uid":44233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇相，個商場嘅格局，地方大，走廊闊，空曠平地大<br />\n如果有心做，我覺得應該有得救<br />\n而家九成九嘅商場來來去去都係嗰啲連鎖品牌鋪頭<br />\n做類似葵涌廣場模式嘅商場<br />\n仲要完全冇連鎖品牌嘅鋪頭<br />\n食肆比例比葵廣更多<br />\n最好可以做到大笪地個種平民地道味道<br />\n再加大量經營有特色小遊戲嘅攤檔，好似遊樂場果啲<br />\n（唔好又係歡樂天地嗰啲喇)<br />\n我覺得會吸引到區外嘅家庭嚟食同玩</blockquote><br />\n已經急不及待想玩玩了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158420814509089933cb7a33ee490ffd47b1d856","tid":233280,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"以前灣景都死過一排啦<br />\n宜家有吉之島旺到仆街"},{"pid":"32261bfd1996f0522f2fc4a6ec9c661385b81a38","tid":233280,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實個死因係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照計附近啲人都係度架</blockquote><br />\n海濱廣場（英語：Riviera Plaza）位於香港荃灣區海濱花園內，於1990年11月落成，商場樓高9層（地下及1-8樓）和設有2層地庫，總樓面為242,685平方呎，並提供171個車位。商場曾經擁有佔地3層的永安百貨、翰騰閣酒家以及美食廣場等眾多設施。然而因交通不便，以及居民亦甚少到該商場消費，商場於1997年後開始出現大量店舖凋空的情況。商場於2012年11月成功以5.08億港元售出，2013年11月後一直封閉至今。</blockquote><br />\n唔係話死過人係花槽跟住鬧鬼無人去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對面已經係墳場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次拜完山去先知有依個商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:細個住荃灣超過10年"},{"pid":"41f3505b8b67996de12dbc692966f444ebd40dc2","tid":233280,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:00:05.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"71ff1cd1c818438601781cb696107e5b9d21e57a","tid":233280,"uid":5539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"扑野有冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db27631142c3f8cd7c7530455b66397761e6c53d","tid":233280,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T18:29:20.000Z","msg":"末移民住過 ，果陣時仲好熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bc1fd6caab12193720f0bd9037097747290e7d","tid":233280,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扑野有冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入到去咩?"},{"pid":"94df56fa946d97ceae6af6c011a48e126dc7e3e1","tid":233280,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1af2a3bd2d30ce0fa03d0c00735cf1dcce9b21","tid":233280,"uid":16353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:18:00.000Z","msg":"以前得番溜冰場果陣 仲有同d中學同學去玩 覺得靜靜地都唔錯"},{"pid":"6935676591f27eff40de33cc9fa56ad3b614d9d9","tid":233280,"uid":36822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:23:43.000Z","msg":"細個年年拜完山都會去"},{"pid":"6f7122b0216deefa1677d2cf94075b02edc01345","tid":233280,"uid":10568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入去玩running man</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3定4年前係舊登組人玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣玩溜冰場果兩層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <