/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912aebc4fdf00b846fde19773a025fe9175761b7","tid":233280,"uid":25329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:38:36.000Z","msg":"原來幾年冇入過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前會去幫襯M記"},{"pid":"adccbbfe6a18c1de208765d0ddf3540ce6e5dd48","tid":233280,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:41:05.000Z","msg":"qe"},{"pid":"529ccc077dba84c8f27efca21781dc91ad7d4a85","tid":233280,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T20:41:52.000Z","msg":"搬左4年<br />\n依家先知m記都收埋皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c62e09f503ddf148846bb62c3eede062ed20304","tid":233280,"uid":55601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T21:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪真係咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前頂樓仲有開燈會同frd上去玩卡<br />\n後尾燈都唔開就恐怖到唔敢上去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到搬走前淨係會去同一層既m記同百佳 其他層完全冇再上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次同老豆呀爺一齊 老豆話咦好似咁耐都未上過頂樓 跟住一齊搭𨋢 上到去得幾盞射燈開著 老豆行出𨋢望兩眼話 乜尻嚟㗎 跟住就一齊落翻樓下<br />\n隔冇幾耐個場就封咗了"},{"pid":"c7bb4e8988bd04e0c722cef265b998bbd8918f16","tid":233280,"uid":87134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T22:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正正住喺隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我陣係想要返個m記炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n環宇海灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係個商場exact7ly喺隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n17座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n好多座都好近嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbe52c3fa3551a5e8d02a163b475892db8587e4","tid":233280,"uid":20547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:26:32.000Z","msg":"以前有m記食 依家係海濱淨係食陸記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92e35b7281fef087ac8bf7d980ceb67e3d82b2d","tid":233280,"uid":17042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T23:27:53.000Z","msg":"仆街 有次諗住同fd撘lift 直上7,8樓玩 <br />\n(嗰陣仲未封7,8樓粒制）<br />\n點知上到去 個lift 門開咗唔夠3秒...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就俾個實Q係樓下撳返部lift落去3樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}